trans-unit.source: Indicates how a <xref href="System.Windows.Media.Animation.ParallelTimeline"></xref> will behave when one or more of its <xref href="System.Windows.Media.Animation.Timeline"></xref> children slips.
trans-unit.target: 나타냅니다 어떻게는 <xref href="System.Windows.Media.Animation.ParallelTimeline"> </xref> 있을 때 동작 하의 하나 이상의 해당 <xref href="System.Windows.Media.Animation.Timeline"> </xref> 자식이 지연 되 합니다.

trans-unit.source: Indicates that a <xref href="System.Windows.Media.Animation.ParallelTimeline"></xref> will not slip with the child <xref href="System.Windows.Media.Animation.Timeline"></xref>, but will expand to fit all slipping <xref href="System.Windows.Media.Animation.Timeline"></xref> children.
trans-unit.target: 나타냅니다는 <xref href="System.Windows.Media.Animation.ParallelTimeline"> </xref> 자식 함께 지연 <xref href="System.Windows.Media.Animation.Timeline"> </xref>, 지연 되는 모든 맞게 확장 됨 하지만 <xref href="System.Windows.Media.Animation.Timeline"> </xref> 자식 합니다.

trans-unit.source: **NOTE**: This is only effective when the <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Timeline.Duration*> of the <xref href="System.Windows.Media.Animation.ParallelTimeline"></xref> is not explicitly specified.

Indicates that a <xref href="System.Windows.Media.Animation.ParallelTimeline"></xref> will slip along with its first child <xref href="System.Windows.Media.Animation.Timeline"></xref> that can slip whenever that child is delayed or accelerated..
trans-unit.target: 나타냅니다는 <xref href="System.Windows.Media.Animation.ParallelTimeline"> </xref> 첫 번째 자식과 함께 지연 됨 <xref href="System.Windows.Media.Animation.Timeline"> </xref> 해당 자식이 지연 되거나 가속 될 때마다 지연 될 수 있는...
